data.description: Back on Market. Cute Bungalow located in Davenport's McClellan Park subdivision! Conveniently located close schools, shopping, dining, park, golf course & other recreation. Lots of updates in recent years. Relax on the front porch, enjoy the open floor plan with the living & dining room combo with updated wood floors. Enjoy cooking in the completely updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar & beautiful counter tops & wood cabinets....there is even a flat screen TV. The Master bedroom features a large closet & private 3/4 bath. Upstairs bedroom has extra storage and would also make a great office. Basement has laundry area, 3/4 bath & storage room. 2 car garage in level backyard. Per seller-many updates in 2012 include: new roof, new windows on main floor, updated kitchen and main floor bathrooms, wood floors & carpet.  Make your appt today!
